OL,3,CRail Minister reports himself to
OL,4,Cpolice for using phone while driving
OL,6,FHe was reported to police on March 31
OL,7,Fby one of the passengers on this
OL,8,Fyear's tour, which had taken place
OL,9,Fthree days earlier, after he texted a
OL,10,Ffriend about a prostate cancer test
OL,11,Fwhile driving.
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police confirmed that
OL,14,Fthe investigation was initially closed
OL,15,Fdue to lack of evidence, but has been
OL,16,Freopened after Lord Hendy admitted
OL,17,Fusing his phone behind the wheel.
