OL,3,CRail Minister reports himself to
OL,4,Cpolice for using phone while driving
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Lord Hendy said:
OL,7,F"Last month Peter Hendy used his phone
OL,8,Fwhile driving. He has apologised in
OL,9,Ffull for this error of judgment and
OL,10,Fhas contacted the police."
OL,12,FHe is likely to receive a fine and six
OL,13,Fpoints on his licence as a result.
OL,15,FThe organisers of the Railway Family
OL,16,Ffundraiser said the group had "always
OL,17,Fbeen grateful to Lord Hendy" for his
OL,18,Fsupport and had not received any
OL,19,Fformal complaint about him at the time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
