OL,6,FThey said: "Since then, the organisers
OL,7,Fhave only had one conversation from
OL,8,Fthe complainant in the form of a text
OL,9,Fmessage, which he sent on April 2,
OL,10,Fwhere he informed us that he'd
OL,11,Freported Lord Hendy to the
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police.
OL,14,F"The Railway Family fundraiser is run
OL,15,Fby railway professionals, all of whom
OL,16,Fwork with safe systems of work and
OL,17,Frules and regulations about safe
OL,18,Fpractice.
