OL,3,CRail Minister reports himself to
OL,4,Cpolice for using phone while driving
OL,6,F"None of us would advocate or condone
OL,7,Funsafe practices. However, we
OL,8,Freiterate that we are not aware of the
OL,9,Fwhole situation, and affirm our hope
OL,10,Fthat any investigation is able to be
OL,11,Fconducted fairly.
OL,13,F"The organisers regret that a positive
OL,14,Fand enjoyable event ended in this way
OL,15,Fand would once again like to express
OL,16,Four thanks to Lord Hendy for his
OL,17,Fsupport for our event and fundraising."
